respectively (mole ratio). These will be calculated from the percent by =
mass=20
determined for of K, Fe, C<SUB>2</SUB>O<SUB>4</SUB>, and H<SUB>2</SUB>O =
in the=20
experiments listed below:&nbsp; </SPAN></P>
<P class=3DMsoNormal><SPAN style=3D"FONT-SIZE: 12pt"></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>
<P class=3DMsoNormal style=3D"MARGIN-LEFT: 0.75in; TEXT-INDENT: =
-0.25in"><SPAN=20
style=3D"FONT-SIZE: 12pt">1.<SPAN=20
style=3D"FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=20
</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=3D"FONT-SIZE: 12pt">The team=92s procedure for =
